headline: Smucker Q3 Earnings Beat Estimates, Sales Up 7% on Pricing Gains
summary: SJM tops Q3 estimates as 7% sales growth and strong coffee pricing offset cost pressures, while earnings dip y/y due to higher green coffee and tariffs.
